event RoleAdminChanged(bytes32 indexed role, bytes32 indexed previousAdminRole, bytes32 indexed newAdminRole)
event RoleGranted(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
event RoleRevoked(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
function createBridgeToken(string name_, string symbol_, uint8 decimals_, address owner, uint256 salt) returns (address)

function getBridgeTokenAddress(address owner, uint256 salt) view returns (address)
function getMintBurnGatewayAddress(address owner, uint256 salt) view returns (address)
function getPoolGatewayAddress(address owner, uint256 salt) view returns (address)
function hasRole(bytes32 role, address account) view returns (bool)
